# Runtime and private memory
memory/user/*
memory/projects/*
memory/runtime/*
state/*
reports/task-reports/*
reports/verification-reports/*
reports/user-reports/*
pals/*/state/*
pals/*/reports/*
pals/*/memory/*.local.md
contacts/collaboration-memory.md
